# BER Data

This GitHub organization hosts schemas, registries, and supporting tooling for the data lakehouses of the U.S. Department of Energy's Biological and Environmental Research (BER) program.

Schemas are authored in [LinkML](https://linkml.io), a YAML-based modeling language for describing the structure of data. Registries catalog the datasets, studies, instruments, and vocabularies used across BER lakehouses.

## Primary Resources

- **Documentation:** [ber-data.github.io](https://ber-data.github.io)
- **Lakehouse Registry:** [ber-data.github.io/lakehouse-registry](https://ber-data.github.io/lakehouse-registry/)
- **Modeling language:** [LinkML](https://linkml.io)
- **Program:** [DOE Biological and Environmental Research](https://science.osti.gov/ber)

